content: I think I'll try out Mint and YNAB to see which one I like better. I've heard good things about both of them. By the way, since I've been watching a lot of YouTube videos lately, do you think it's possible to make money from watching videos? I've seen some videos on James Charles' channel where he talks about brand deals and sponsorships, and I was wondering if that's something that's only possible for big YouTubers or if there are other ways to make money from watching videos.
